OL,3,CWest Midlands Police and Crime
OL,4,CCommissioner role scrapped as Mayor
OL,5,Cset to take over
OL,7,FThe West Midlands Police and Crime
OL,8,FCommissioner (PCC) role has been
OL,9,Fscrapped, with the region's Mayor set
OL,10,Fto take over.
OL,12,FIn a statement on X, posted on
OL,13,FWednesday 6 December, Andy Street said
OL,14,Fthe Home Secretary had agreed to
OL,15,Ftransfer powers from the current PCC,
OL,16,FSimon Foster, to himself.
OL,18,FHe added: "Crime has doubled in 8
OL,19,Fyears and our force is now in special
OL,20,Fmeasures. We cannot go on like this.
